TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message confront bio vizier
TriggerLogic.Message: At the West end of the area, the Bio Vizier is trying to escape on a starship. The ship will arrive in 15 minutes. Ada must confront him before the starship arrive.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message defend everything defend nothing
TriggerLogic.Message: The area is filled with defense. However, the acient art of war did say "He who defends everything defends nothing" Use scouts and planes to find a weak spot in their defense and break through there.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message Reinforcement
TriggerLogic.Message: Since there is no time to collect resources or build units, you will recieve reinforcement every 90 seconds.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message defense need nergy to operate
TriggerLogic.Message: The most critical defenses need energy to operate. Target these power plant to disable the defenses and you can secure a shorter route for your reinforcement.

TriggerLogic.Name: Convo Message cloaked AA scout
